Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:54.59,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.74,0:02:08.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:15.17,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... I want it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:16.58,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:20.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease me...
