Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.55,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you stop\Nin the middle like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.61,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to say my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.61,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:06.28,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What difference does\Nit make if I say your name!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:11.19,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,My name and my\Nbody don't belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:12.29,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.43,0:04:17.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone\Nbut her defile them.
