Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.11,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Class is cancelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.82,0:05:18.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I came all the way\Nhere in this heat for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:19.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:23.26,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuro!\NThey cancelled fourth period.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:26.68,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? That's the\Nonly reason I'm here today!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.09,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:31.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:35.14,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,See that guy?\NThat's Yoshiko's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:39.30,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? But, that's\Nnot Yoshiko with him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.12,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she said\Nhis name was Amemiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:43.62,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:47.11,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of our business, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.59,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the cafeteria.\NI'll buy you lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:54.97,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I wish I could,\Nbut I have to go to the clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:55.96,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tatsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:06:00.31,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal. Don't apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:03.60,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I'm glad\Nthat you like the earrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:05.67,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,They look really good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.78,0:06:07.50,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:24.92,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:27.39,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.97,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.37,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.28,0:06:46.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.88,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you dating Yoshiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I am. What's it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:55.85,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you\Ndoing in the clubroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:58.62,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NWere you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:00.25,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you\Nfigure it out for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.63,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't watching! Why would I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:12.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I was having sex with another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.77,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:16.02,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:18.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel sorry for Yoshiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.24,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:20.78,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:23.92,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.25,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiko loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:26.69,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:32.90,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you want anyone else?\NEither a girl, or a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.96,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy says he loves me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.83,0:07:40.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What difference does it make\Nwhether it's a girl or a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:42.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,A hole is a hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.47,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:46.57,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You can still screw girls\Nafter you've screwed a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:47.89,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting\Nso worked up over this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:52.88,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.22,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't kid yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.55,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could have feelings for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:58.18,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me\Nto screw you, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.35,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the ride of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:08.09,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,All I feel for you is pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:11.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never really\Nloved anyone, have you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:19.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I truly love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:22.74,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.25,0:08:29.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I ran into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.88,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kaname?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.51,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.56,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You and Tatsuro are\Nhaving problems, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:40.48,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to steal my Amemiya\Njust to get even with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:42.26,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know\Nwhat you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.26,0:08:44.43,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuro and I are doing just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:47.78,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, he just gave me these.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those are really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:52.06,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's too hot\Nout here, so we'll get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:55.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Kaname!\NRemember, we're still on for Friday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.44,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00ff9900&}Yosh-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya, sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.25,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be such a bitch sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.42,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll forgive me,\NI won't ever do it again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:09.15,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be\Nwith a guy like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.66,0:09:10.65,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.32,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:42.58,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a year since\Nwe said goodbye to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:45.12,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that work keeps you busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:46.46,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:48.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you call me, at least?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.39,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,A single postcard is not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.96,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.10,0:09:56.23,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:09:59.57,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:03.24,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you say\Nthose words to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:14.58,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is here to take your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:18.43,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your name and number\Nat the sound of the tone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we'll get back to you\Nas soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:27.13,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Leona.\NCome to my office tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:31.23,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something for you from\Nyour sister. I'll be expecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:53.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that new\Nbistro is pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:54.89,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,The food is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:56.68,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been written\Nup in all the magazines!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:58.57,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I ate so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.87,0:11:01.30,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:08.82,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Amemiya, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.11,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.95,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks like a movie star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:22.92,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I should ask him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:24.19,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just snatch him like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:29.96,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But he did it with one of my\Nclassmates and she can't stop bragging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.63,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,And he looks like he really\Nknows how to kiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:36.03,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I would love to kiss Amemiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:10.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you today?\NYou're acting funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:13.10,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because your kisses\Nare so wonderful, Tatsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.81,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.04,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:25.98,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend was talking about that\NAmemiya. She said he's pretty kinky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:27.35,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinky?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:31.92,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He goes both ways. He does\Nit with guys and girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:37.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,We know about\NYoshiko and that other girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:39.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...but there are\Nprobably a lot of others, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:40.77,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:44.23,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But, do you think\NYoshiko knows this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:45.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:47.81,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,We are talking\Nabout Yoshiko, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.43,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she doesn't care at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.30,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she cares!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.95,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so sensitive?\NThat's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:01.19,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I concerned with that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:07.04,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuro, do you really love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.32,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:10.83,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:15.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:21.22,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really are\Nacting funny today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:24.50,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. Hold me tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.81,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy doesn't\Nhave anything to do with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:39.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,When it's your sister, you always\Nget here on time, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.43,0:13:41.44,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you get back to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:42.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:44.56,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. From your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:52.41,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So, don't you want to know how\Nshe's doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.01,0:13:54.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she well?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:56.12,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.48,0:14:00.88,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment, she's the top\NJapanese model in the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.92,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she ask about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.72,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.12,0:14:12.11,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,She picked that out herself\Nduring one of her rare breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:18.45,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead. See how it looks on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:26.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever she's interviewed\Nshe mentions your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:29.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it is a strange name,\Nshe says she likes it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:34.66,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she'll be coming\Nhome any time soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:37.24,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:42.15,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you.\NYour sister has good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:47.39,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of the top\Nmodels in Paris and Milan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.62,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a critical time for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.06,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:55.94,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your sister's dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:59.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how badly\Nyou want to see her...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:02.14,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you'll have\Nto be patient a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:07.24,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I, however, can't wait anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:21.96,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I love both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:26.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,She's very beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:27.50,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,As are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:32.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's dream... I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:36.21,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But, let me share in the dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:40.28,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be part of her dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:42.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Having to live without her is unfair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you want\Nto know about Amemiya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of guy is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.05,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:58.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he like when he's\Nalone with you? Is he nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.37,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,If he gets mad, he won't even\Ntalk to me when we're on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of cute, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:08.78,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always looking in a mirror\Nand that narcissism is kind of a turn-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:10.90,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he is pretty self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:16.80,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But, hey Yoshiko, haven't you\Nheard what people say about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.69,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That he goes both ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:20.17,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:21.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.39,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But, who cares if it's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:25.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It just means he's\Nthat much better at sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.69,0:16:27.99,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.13,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname, you're adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.27,0:16:34.45,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sexual prowess is\Nan important thing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:39.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I love it when we walk down\Nthe street and other girls get jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.29,0:16:41.77,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that ever happen\Nwhen you're with Tatsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.91,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.56,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:50.51,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't happen, but he loves me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.25,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:59.49,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, there is one\Nthing that really ticks Amemiya off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.86,0:17:00.49,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:04.23,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling him by his first name.\NCalling him Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.06,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:07.20,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:11.27,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He gets mad and says,\N"That name belongs to her!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:12.44,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,"Her"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:14.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably some problem\Nhe had with an old girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't been able to forget\Nabout her or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.01,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he say\Nanything more than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.11,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never asked for more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.28,0:17:23.25,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why spoil the fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.98,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just not right! It's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:30.55,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one getting all worked\Nup and you're calling me weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:33.53,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... worked up because\NI care about you, Yoshiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:36.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep this up, you're going\Nto end up with a broken heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be\Nserious about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.73,0:17:40.89,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives you the right\Nto say something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:46.54,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why does it matter?\NWe're not hurting anyone, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:53.78,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But do you really love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:57.34,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are weird, Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:02.22,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that you've got the\Nhots for Amemiya yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.42,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,That just isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:11.69,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I was supposed to\Nmeet Yuko and the girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:14.02,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kaname!\NPay my tab, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:14.83,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.80,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never fall for a guy like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.35,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I when I have Tatsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.61,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuro loves me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:00.87,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I'm relieved\Nthat you like the earrings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:02.84,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,They look really good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:44.16,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Come up to my place\Nand get out of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:45.25,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.69,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll get in touch with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.38,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, screw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:12.36,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:15.09,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend has\Nbeen cheating on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:16.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:17.99,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:21.75,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do it with the\Nmost disgusting guy I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:24.29,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:05.13,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:08.07,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.79,0:22:04.86,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.23,0:22:09.93,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:12.57,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:14.64,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You're driving me crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.88,0:22:17.31,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,You want it that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.46,0:22:29.35,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll give it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:38.32,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:40.42,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I do like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:45.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.10,0:23:54.23,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I care nothing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.39,0:24:06.38,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.82,0:24:10.26,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:22.70,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.92,0:24:39.11,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.29,0:24:41.72,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.16,0:24:44.76,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.80,0:24:49.49,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to fall in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.84,0:25:07.38,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one person I truly love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.03,0:25:14.61,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,But, she's the one\Nperson I can't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.59,0:25:24.72,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister, my soul is so thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.63,0:28:04.00,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is here to take your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.88,0:28:06.18,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.33,0:28:10.73,Fansub,,0000,0000,0000,,Amemiya, who are\Nyou sleeping with tonight?
